    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>At Stock Operator, your privacy and data security are very important to us. This policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information.</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Personal details (name, email, phone) when you register or contact us.</li>
      <li>Payment information for plan subscriptions.</li>
      <li>Trading-related data when using our funded accounts.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Your Data</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To provide and manage funded trading accounts.</li>
      <li>To process payments and issue invoices.</li>
      <li>To communicate updates, promotions, or support messages.</li>
      <li>To comply with legal and regulatory obligations.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Protection</h2>
    <p>We use industry-standard encryption and security measures to safeguard your information. Your data will not be sold or shared with third parties without your consent.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Access your personal data.</li>
      <li>Request corrections or deletions.</li>
      <li>Opt out of marketing communications.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>For questions regarding this Privacy Policy, email us at <a href="mailto:support@stockoperator.com">support@stockoperator.com</a>.</p>
